tweet: Hi Fans! I am pleased to tell you you can now talk to me through Twitter!
Pinkg Kwok, if you read this: your chinese food smells like toothpaste in three day old vomit.
Just recorded new demos. Exciting stuff!!
Neighbor tells me by phone I must stop playing my demos or he will keep sticking needles in his temple so the pain will drown out the sound.
Some of the lyrics need a bit of work still. Any fan out there knows the English word for borrelnoot?
